{"tid":2461380,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"法德等召支那大使抗議反制  支那外交部：不惹事也不怕事","createTime":"2021-03-25T11:30:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T12:42:51.000Z","uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cfe50ca4a5f159f89a7b5689211e1ead4a633d01","tid":2461380,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T11:30:31.000Z","msg":"歐盟制裁中國新疆四名官員和一個實體後，中國採取反制，制裁共十位歐洲議會成員和歐盟機構。中方召見外國大使抗議後，法國、德國等歐盟等國再召中國大使抗議。中國外交部發言人回應指，歐方一些國家的做法無理，完全不接受。歐盟成員匈牙利指，歐盟對中方制裁是妄自尊大的體現，只會破壞歐盟與中國的關係。<br />\n<br />\n  法國外交部傳召中國駐法大使盧沙野，不過由於日前已傳召過中國大使，遭回：「大使沒空，有事兒明天再說」。法國外交部稱中方的制裁決定「令人無法接受」，揚言將再次傳召中國駐法大使盧沙野。德國亦傳召了駐柏林的中國大使，指中方的反制裁措施是針對立法機關議員和學者的制裁，完全不能接受。而中國大使吳懇亦就歐對華制裁，向德方提出嚴正交涉。丹麥外相科弗德亦發表聲明表示，中方的制裁措施顯然是對自由表達意見的攻擊。<br />\n<br />\n  中國外交部批評歐盟持雙重標準，以謊言及虛假信息任意制裁，卻不許中方還嘴還手，是霸凌、霸道及虛偽表現。外交部發言人華春瑩指：「中方不惹事、不挑事也不怕事，不會被訛詐。」"},{"pid":"f9424e8bcfaa77df75c280d95f8de7058839ff39","tid":2461380,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T11:32:58.000Z","msg":"戰狼外交叫不惹事？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/xi-04242020051858.html/123.png/@@images/image/social_media\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fcantonese%2Fnews%2Fxi-04242020051858.html%2F123.png%2F%40%40images%2Fimage%2Fsocial_media&h=129904b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pub.creaders.net/upload_files/image/202103/20210323_16165390824607.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpub.creaders.net%2Fupload_files%2Fimage%2F202103%2F20210323_16165390824607.png&h=969b63b7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"264785049916645c168f59914bb10b850e97e3a6","tid":2461380,"uid":196671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T11:33:29.000Z","msg":"又係匈牙利Viktor Orban條撚專制奶共走狗撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c52eb03d58ef4b4b6c9c475ea51abd3d8d20f871","tid":2461380,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T11:35:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f36f74133c5b52ca01c3214301ebae223441ab8","tid":2461380,"uid":337498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T11:43:33.000Z","msg":"姐係點，你制裁左人，人地制裁翻你，你抗咩議？有D骨氣同支那鬥制裁啦屌。等到時支那來求翻你地唔好制裁佢，等支那7下先啱呀嘛。結果你地7左先。"},{"pid":"594593d9786521928e2436113daebf5b002f887e","tid":2461380,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T12:42:51.000Z","msg":"崩牙駒:「無事唔好搞事 有事唔好怕事」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xw5bsYwvU6s&amp;ab_channel=%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C%E5%8B%95%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9EHKAppleDaily\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dxw5bsYwvU6s%26ab_channel%3D%25E8%2598%258B%25E6%259E%259C%25E5%258B%2595%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259EHKAppleDaily&d=Vr1Lb3BWhK3V%2BSmIqtN%2B%2FoTtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=4f862a53\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xw5bsYwvU6s&amp;ab_channel=%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C%E5%8B%95%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9EHKAppleDaily</a>"}]}